+     * <br> |SUBJECT       |EQUAL_TO        |Registration code                                       |
+     * <br> |SENT_DATE     |GREATER_THAN    |1970-01-01T00:00:00.000Z                                |
+     * <br> |RECEIVED_DATE |LESS_THAN       |2020-06-14T11:47:11.521Z                                |
